Good morning everyone. Wow, it's so nice to have a warm house again. This morning's temp is 28, so they restored power just in time.

Going on 3 days with no power after that blast of a wind storm. Hoping to see lights today.
The storm is taking its toll. Worst one for years. We're still in the dark. House temp is 60. Gas fireplace isn't much help either. Yikes
Power's still out. Going on 4 hours now. Keep forgetting how much we depend on electricity. At least I knocked a chapter out before it did.
Wind storm kicked us off the grid. Loosing shingles too. At least I saved my work.
